# Sophia Price

## Senior HR Coordinator Center Operations & Administration

Phone: **512-475-9411** |
Email: **[sprice@tacc.utexas.edu](mailto:sprice@tacc.utexas.edu)**

Sophia Price joined TACC in 2019 as a member of the Center Operations & Administration Team. Sophia will oversee recruitment, onboarding, performance management, timekeeping, along with many other HR processes as TACC continues to grow. She has previously worked at UT in the Center for Petroleum and Geosystems Engineering (CPGE), Bureau of Economic Geology (BEG), and Graduate School.

### Education

**B.A., Human Resource Management**  

Concordia University